{"id":1540,"date":"2022-09-01T12:50:37","date_gmt":"2022-09-01T16:50:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1540"},"modified":"2023-06-12T15:26:27","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T19:26:27","slug":"bruno-lamarche","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/bruno-lamarche\/","title":{"rendered":"Bruno Lamarche"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1374\">Bruno Lamarche est un saxophoniste, clarinettiste et fl\u00fbtiste cr\u00e9atif qui poursuit une carri\u00e8re musicale fort enrichissante depuis plus de vingt-cinq ans<\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"896\"><span class=\"id_817cebe5-6416-418e-a497-7d1f3ff306d0-68\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">.<\/span><\/span> <span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1165\">On a pu <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1166\"><span class=\"id_8eada136-1423-4321-ba0f-3dc38182dc71-38\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">l\u2019<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1167\">entendre sur disque entre autres avec\u00a0<\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1168\"><span class=\"id_8eada136-1423-4321-ba0f-3dc38182dc71-39\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">:<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1169\"> son groupe Buddhakick,<\/span>\u00a0<span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1218\">Sussex,<\/span>\u00a0<span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1267\">Mandala de Joel Miller (Prix Opus du meilleur concert jazz\/musique du monde), <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1316\">F\u00e9lix <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1317\"><span class=\"id_347d2199-5ebc-44d5-a235-f966ec64b624-14\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">St\u00fcssi<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1318\"> 5 &amp; Ray Anderson (nomin\u00e9 aux prix Juno et grand prix de Jazz General Motors),<\/span>\u00a0<span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1367\">Roberto Lopez<\/span>\u00a0<span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"672\">et avec Bernard Primeau (Liaisons)<\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"673\"><span class=\"id_ba34c979-405d-49a2-accc-a48eb78c4342-12\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">.<\/span><\/span> <span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1000\">Il a eu <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1001\"><span class=\"id_f9262915-ca6a-40c8-93ff-5e7ab68cb4f7-164\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">l\u2019<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1002\">honneur de jouer avec de grands musiciens tels <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1003\"><span class=\"id_f9262915-ca6a-40c8-93ff-5e7ab68cb4f7-165\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">Ben<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1004\"> Monder, David Binney, Kurt Rosenwinkel, Beno\u00eet Charest, Christine Duncan, et Don Thompson, Jordan Officer, et au sein de groupes tels l\u2019OSM, le terrible orchestre de Belleville, Sussex, le Dixieband, Altsys, l\u2019Orchestre National de Jazz de Montr\u00e9al, le Jazzlab et l\u2019Afro-Columbian Jazz Orchestra, et ce, dans <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1005\"><span class=\"id_f9262915-ca6a-40c8-93ff-5e7ab68cb4f7-167\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">14<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1006\"> pays diff\u00e9rents.<\/span> <span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1056\">Arrangeur reconnu, <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1057\"><span class=\"id_99b97918-793e-48f2-893f-4ad39a16c067-96\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">M.<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1058\"> Lamarche a \u00e9t\u00e9 boursier du CALQ et a obtenu un baccalaur\u00e9at en interpr\u00e9tation du Jazz \u00e0 <\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1059\"><span class=\"id_99b97918-793e-48f2-893f-4ad39a16c067-97\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">l\u2019<\/span><\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1060\">Universit\u00e9 McGill (avec haute distinction), o\u00f9 il a re\u00e7u le Marion Magor Memorial Scholarship et le James McGill Award<\/span><span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"1061\"><span class=\"id_99b97918-793e-48f2-893f-4ad39a16c067-117\" data-slate-object=\"mark\" data-info=\"noeud\">.<\/span><\/span> <span data-slate-object=\"text\" data-key=\"693\" data-slate-fragment=\"\">Aussi actif dans l\u2019enseignement du Jazz, il enseigne pr\u00e9sentement au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent, a donn\u00e9 des classes de ma\u00eetre dans plus d\u2019une douzaine d\u2019\u00e9coles secondaires, et a dirig\u00e9 des orchestres de jazz, dont l\u2019Ensemble Jazz de Montr\u00e9al.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1541,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[206],"specialite-equipe":[226,239,266,270,2267],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1540","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-musique","specialite-equipe-vents","specialite-equipe-flute-traversiere","specialite-equipe-clarinette-jazz","specialite-equipe-saxophone-jazz","specialite-equipe-musique-classique"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1540","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1541"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1540"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=1540"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=1540"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=1540"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=1540"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}